OL,3,CEx-firefighter admits taking photo of
OL,4,Cdead man at scene of crash
OL,6,FA former firefighter has admitted
OL,7,Ftaking a photograph of a dead man at
OL,8,Fthe scene of a crash.
OL,10,FCameron Hancel, 33, pleaded guilty at
OL,11,FWolverhampton Crown Court to
OL,12,Fmisconducting himself in public office
OL,13,Fwhile working for West Midlands Fire
OL,14,FService on 13 March last year, by
OL,15,Ftaking a photo of the victim and
OL,16,Fsending it to others.
OL,18,FA second charge under the 2003
OL,19,FCommunications Act was withdrawn by
OL,20,Fthe prosecution.
