OL,3,CEx-firefighter admits taking photo of
OL,4,Cdead man at scene of crash
OL,6,FHancel, of Chichester Drive, Rowley
OL,7,FRegis, stood in the dock wearing a
OL,8,Fgrey jumper, white shirt and dark
OL,9,Ftrousers, and spoke only to confirm
OL,10,Fhis name and enter his plea during the
OL,11,Fshort hearing.
OL,13,FThe court heard he is of good
OL,14,Fcharacter and has never been in
OL,15,Ftrouble before.
OL,17,FJudge Talog Davies accepted a request
OL,18,Ffrom Hancel's defence to adjourn
OL,19,Fsentencing for a pre-sentence report
OL,20,Fto be compiled by probation officers.
