OL,4,Cdead man at scene of crash
OL,6,FAddressing Hancel, who was released on
OL,7,Funconditional bail, the judge said:
OL,8,F"Following that plea, I am adjourning
OL,9,Fyour sentence until October 4.
OL,11,F"I am ordering the Probation Service
OL,12,Fto prepare a pre-sentence report. All
OL,13,Foptions will remain open."
OL,15,FHancel hid his face under a baseball
OL,16,Fcap as he left the court building
OL,17,Faround two hours after his hearing had
OL,18,Ffinished and avoided questions from
OL,19,Fwaiting reporters.
