OL,3,CEx-firefighter admits taking photo of
OL,4,Cdead man at scene of crash
OL,6,FWest Midlands Fire Service dismissed
OL,7,FHancel in August 2023 after being made
OL,8,Faware of the incident.
OL,10,FIn a statement, a spokesman said:
OL,11,F"There is no place in our service for
OL,12,Fpeople who undertake such actions.
OL,14,F"His conduct compounded the grief of
OL,15,Fthe victim's family and loved ones,
OL,16,Fand they remain in our thoughts."
